            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
                An elegant, lightweight PHP framework for composing beautiful, modern web applications with speed and precision.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="{{ base_url }}/docs/installation" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                    Get Started
